    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sheet tin utensils with vertical sides and an inner and outer ring used to shape doughnuts, often with an attached handle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
